OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine and
OL,6,Fdry evening for much of the region
OL,7,Fwith some sunny intervals. Patchy
OL,8,Fcloud becomes widespread from the
OL,9,Fnorth overnight with a chance of
OL,10,Foutbreaks of drizzle. Light northerly
OL,11,Fwinds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FA bright start away from the
OL,14,Feast, though increasingly cloudy
OL,15,Fthrough the morning. Patchy drizzle,
OL,16,Fparticularly for coastal areas. Sunny
OL,17,Fintervals developing later. Cooler
OL,18,Fthan recent days. Light northerly
OL,19,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
