OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FA dry
OL,6,Fand fine day on Sunday. Turning
OL,7,Fcloudier with patchy rain for coastal
OL,8,Fareas through Monday and Tuesday.
OL,9,FRemaining warm inland, cooler along
OL,10,Fthe coasts. Light northerly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
